    "Id": "chassisdef_kumazemi_KUZ-D7",
    "Name": "Kumazemi",
    "Details": "The KUZ-D7 builds on the KUZ-D5 by trading its SRM-4 and ER Large Laser for an ER PPC and a pair of additional ER Medium Lasers, giving it three ER Medium Lasers in total alongside its AC/20, Artemis-guided LRM-15, and new ER PPC. A Guardian ECM Suite has also been added for electronic protection. To accommodate these changes, the KUZ-D7 switches to Light Ferro-Fibrous armor and carries a reduced LRM ammunition reserve, though it retains the Endo Steel structure and double heat sinks introduced on the KUZ-D5.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Rugged</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.14</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Lower, Right Lower</color>",
